  "transcript": {
    "language": "en",
    "is_generated": false,
    "segments": [
      {
        "start": 0.1,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "- [David] Just as I suspected wordsmiths,"
      },
      {
        "start": 2.3,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "you're watching a video about vocabulary."
      },
      {
        "start": 4.5,
        "duration": 3.1,
        "text": "I bet that means you\nhate math and science."
      },
      {
        "start": 7.6,
        "duration": 3.5,
        "text": "Oh! No, is that not, is\nthat not true for you?"
      },
      {
        "start": 11.1,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "Sorry, wordsmiths, I guess\nI was stereotyping you."
      },
      {
        "start": 13.5,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "What's a stereotype you ask?"
      },
      {
        "start": 15.4,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "Well, you're in the\nright place to find out"
      },
      {
        "start": 17.6,
        "duration": 1.5,
        "text": "because our words for this video"
      },
      {
        "start": 19.1,
        "duration": 3.0,
        "text": "are \"stereotype\" and \"obstacle.\""
      },
      {
        "start": 22.1,
        "duration": 1.9,
        "text": "I'll define them both, we'll\ntalk about word origins,"
      },
      {
        "start": 23.9,
        "duration": 3.2,
        "text": "and then we'll use each\nword in a sentence."
      },
      {
        "start": 27.1,
        "duration": 2.0,
        "text": "So first, definitions."
      },
      {
        "start": 30.6,
        "duration": 2.9,
        "text": "Stereotype. It's a verb and a noun."
      },
      {
        "start": 33.5,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "As a verb, it means to have a fixed idea"
      },
      {
        "start": 35.8,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "about someone or something."
      },
      {
        "start": 38.2,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "I stereotyped you by assuming"
      },
      {
        "start": 40.4,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "that if you're watching a vocab video,"
      },
      {
        "start": 42.8,
        "duration": 3.5,
        "text": "that means you're limited to\nliking one subject in school,"
      },
      {
        "start": 46.3,
        "duration": 1.3,
        "text": "which isn't true."
      },
      {
        "start": 48.5,
        "duration": 2.8,
        "text": "Stereotype is also a\nnoun. It's a fixed idea."
      },
      {
        "start": 51.2,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "Usually about a group or a type of person."
      },
      {
        "start": 53.6,
        "duration": 2.9,
        "text": "And obstacle, which is\nsomething that gets in the way"
      },
      {
        "start": 56.5,
        "duration": 2.9,
        "text": "and keeps you from making progress."
      },
      {
        "start": 59.3,
        "duration": 2.1,
        "text": "All right, time for word origins."
      },
      {
        "start": 61.5,
        "duration": 2.2,
        "text": "So stereotype comes from French."
      },
      {
        "start": 63.6,
        "duration": 2.3,
        "text": "A stereotype is this thing here"
      },
      {
        "start": 65.9,
        "duration": 2.7,
        "text": "from the world of early printed text."
      },
      {
        "start": 68.6,
        "duration": 1.6,
        "text": "Without getting too deep into it,"
      },
      {
        "start": 70.3,
        "duration": 2.1,
        "text": "it was an early kind of photocopy,"
      },
      {
        "start": 72.4,
        "duration": 3.0,
        "text": "a method of simplifying\nthe printing process."
      },
      {
        "start": 75.3,
        "duration": 1.4,
        "text": "From one stereotype,"
      },
      {
        "start": 76.8,
        "duration": 4.7,
        "text": "you could print a text 10,000\ntimes cheaply and easily."
      },
      {
        "start": 81.5,
        "duration": 2.0,
        "text": "But you can't change a stereotype."
      },
      {
        "start": 83.5,
        "duration": 1.5,
        "text": "You can't change the letters around."
      },
      {
        "start": 85.0,
        "duration": 2.4,
        "text": "You can't alter it even slightly."
      },
      {
        "start": 87.4,
        "duration": 2.6,
        "text": "Every print looks exactly the same."
      },
      {
        "start": 90.0,
        "duration": 3.0,
        "text": "The ideas do not change."
      },
      {
        "start": 92.9,
        "duration": 1.4,
